column5: Team 5 is doing a fishing charter on Sunday June 3rd, out of St. Catherines.  There is one spot left if anyone is interested at $125 for a full day, bar b que afterwards.  Setting out from the dock at 6am returning around 2.  PM me if you would like to come along!  Cheers, Jen
Hey Jen have a friend from work who wants to go is that cool     Peace Ken
